data.description: Beautiful home with fresh paint for new owner.  This home has 5 Bedrooms, 3 Full Baths with 1 Bedroom and 1 Full bath on the main floor.  Downstairs with the 1 Bedroom is a Large Greatroom, Kitchen and Eat in Area along The Master bedroom has lots of windows.  Master Bath is spacious with a Huge Walk in Closet.  Lots of square footage for the price.  Located on a cul-de-sac.  Agents please see private notes or call agent for non member showings.
